Name: petey
Comment: Petey is a handsome bantam rooster looking for his forever home!Have you heard about our adoption special?During the month of October, you choose the amount you pay for an adoption (at least $50 suggested) and what your adoption supports. Your donation can assist with special medical care, food & supplies, and owner support for the residents of Santa Cruz County and their companion animals. Your support allows us to save hundreds of additional animal lives and support families and pets in need. Whatever you decide to donate in place of an adoption fee, your new pet will be spayed or neutered, microchipped, vaccinated, and treated for parasites. We want to get every pet off to a healthy start in a new home!
